# SessionMonitor-local gitignore overrides.
#
# The repo-level .gitignore catches *.pubxml across the whole tree, which
# would swallow our intentional publish profile. Re-include it here.
!Properties/PublishProfiles/*.pubxml

# Per-user state lives outside the repo (%LOCALAPPDATA%\CopilotSessionMonitor)
# and the temp self-test log lives in %TEMP%, so neither needs to be listed.
